 death clock begins to count down. Successive homicides that are difficult to crack take place. Yat-chun has to race against time as he wants to change the future by tracking down the perpetrator as soon as possible.","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"276222","season":1,"vote_average":8,"vote_count":1},"modified":"2025-01-10T19:52:20.000Z","cast":["Trần Gia Lạc","Trần Hiểu Hoa","Nguyễn Hạo Tông","Đàm Khải Kỳ","Hà Viễn Đông","Lỗ Chấn Thuận","Văn Tuyết Nhi","Cung Từ Ân","Trần Gia Huy","Janice Pang"],"director":["Sum-Wai Wong"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Trần Gia Lạc","name_vi":"Trần Gia Lạc","name_original":"Carlos Chan Ka-Lok","tmdb_id":1172629,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uCocD9qqMME6ADzKmfaHU6m2eV8.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1172629"},{"name":"Trần Hiểu Hoa","name_vi":"Trần Hiểu Hoa","name_original":"Hera Chan","tmdb_id":2705746,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ntMcYP1NMVxsQcSIcLaGR9JCbtu.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2705746"},{"name":"Nguyễn Hạo Tông","name_vi":"Nguyễn Hạo Tông","name_original":"Nicholas Yuen","tmdb_id":2985584,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jYRVfFP2tUa2qNJa1QRbxwS2TOy.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2985584"},{"name":"Đàm Khải Kỳ","name_vi":"Đàm Khải Kỳ","name_original":"Zoie Tam","tmdb_id":1315729,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rHoeN66q8PBV2TLZdWbmyXQE1Wt.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1315729"},{"name":"Hà Viễn Đông","name_vi":"Hà Viễn Đông","name_original":"Ho Yuen-Tung","tmdb_id":2232032,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/A9CHdVCnwhJAazBUu6NMKklZ9Dk.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2232032"},{"name":"Lỗ Chấn Thuận","name_vi":"Lỗ Chấn Thuận","name_original":"Henry Lo","tmdb_id":1614785,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4SMud7dMceP8EY5rzFYhhGKidwf.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1614785"},{"name":"Văn Tuyết Nhi","name_vi":"Văn Tuyết Nhi","name_original":"Candy Man","tmdb_id